  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to explore whether prophylactic dietary supplementation with prebiotic
      inulin-type fructans is able to influence the intestinal microbiota and the frequency of
      infectious disease episodes in kindergarten children during a winter period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
